msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/180"
msgid "Artillery strike"
msgstr "Artillería"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/date"
msgid "September 27th, 1942 · Stalingrad"
msgstr "27 de septiembre de 1942 - Stalingrado"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/name"
msgid "Pavlov's House <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"
msgstr "La casa de Pavlov <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/name_big"
msgid "Pavlov's House"
msgstr "La casa de Pavlov"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/01"
msgid ""
"What has become of our beloved Stalingrad? The streets of the city are "
"ruined… almost everything has been demolished."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué ha sido de nuestra querida Stalingrado? Las calles de la ciudad están "
"arruinadas... casi todo ha sido destruido."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/02"
msgid ""
"Comrades, I've taken command of the 62nd Army. I tell you this - Stalingrad "
"will decide our fate! I’ll either keep the fascists out of Stalingrad or die "
"trying. There is no land beyond the Volga!"
msgstr ""
"Camaradas, he tomado el mando del 62º Ejército. Os digo esto: ¡Stalingrado "
"decidirá nuestro destino! O mantengo a los fascistas a raya en Stalingrado o "
"moriré en el intento. ¡No existe la Madre Patria más allá del Volga!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/03"
msgid ""
"I do realise your men have been called forward without resupply. You need "
"weapons and ammo. We are going to deal with this situation first. We know "
"for a fact a German depot is nearby."
msgstr ""
"Estoy al tanto de que tus hombres han sido llamados a la linea del frente "
"sin el apropiado reabastecimiento. Necesitais armas y municiones. Vamos a "
"lidiar con esta situación primero. Sabemos que hay un depósito de "
"suministros alemán cerca."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/04"
msgid ""
"Your next objective is to take the strategic apartment building overlooking "
"this entire area."
msgstr ""
"Vuestro siguiente objetivo es tomar el estratégico edificio de apartamentos "
"que domina toda esta zona."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/05"
msgid ""
"Due to our grueling losses, I have put into action Order 166: Offensives are "
"to be organized into small groups with sub-machine guns, hand grenades, and "
"anti-tank rifles. Taking this building is your assignment, Comrades. I will "
"try to get reinforcements for you after the building is in your hands."
msgstr ""
"Debido a nuestras agotadoras pérdidas, he puesto en marcha la Orden 166: Las "
"ofensivas se organizarán en pequeños grupos con subfusiles, granadas de mano "
"y rifles antitanque. Tomar este edificio es vuestra tarea, camaradas. "
"Trataré de conseguir refuerzos después de que el edificio esté en vuestras "
"manos."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/06"
msgid ""
"Good work Comrades. Take positions around this building. The Germans will "
"surely want to take back such a strategic spot."
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, camaradas. Tomad posiciones alrededor del edificio. Los "
"alemanes seguramente querrán recuperar un lugar tan estratégico."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/07"
msgid ""
"I am dispatching Lieutenant Afanasyev from the 3rd Machine Gun Company to "
"reinforce your position. Sergeant Pavlov, you remain in command of this "
"group. Keep your building safe!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy enviando al teniente Afanasyev de la 3ª Compañía de Ametralladoras "
"para reforzar vuestra posición. Sargento Pavlov, usted permanece al mando de "
"este grupo. ¡Mantenga su edificio a salvo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/08"
msgid ""
"I am sending a notorious sniper to reinforce your men, Comrade Pavlov. He in "
"young, but has a reputation among the fascist hordes. Keep him alive and "
"safe."
msgstr ""
"Estoy enviando un francotirador para reforzar a sus hombres, camarada "
"Pavlov. Él es joven, pero ya es famoso y tiene una terrible reputación entre "
"las hordas fascistas. Mantenedle vivo y a salvo."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/09"
msgid ""
"Comrades, engineering supplies have been found left behind by the Germans. I "
"am ordering you to reinforce the approaches of the building to improve its "
"defensive capabilities. "
msgstr ""
"Camaradas, hemos encontrado suministros ingenieriles abandonados por los "
"alemanes. Os ordeno que reforcéis el perímetro del edificio para mejorar su "
"capacidad defensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/10"
msgid ""
"Make our defense unbreakable! All the furious attacks of the Fascist troops "
"will shatter upon these obstacles just like sea waves are broken by granite "
"rock!"
msgstr ""
"¡Haced que nuestra defensa sea inquebrantable! ¡Todos los furiosos ataques "
"de las tropas fascistas serán frenados por nuestros obstáculos como las olas "
"del mar rompen en la orilla!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/11"
msgid ""
"That's it, Comrades. We are winning. Every German soldier must be made to "
"feel that he is living under the muzzle of a Russian gun."
msgstr ""
"Eso es, camaradas. Estamos ganando. Hay que hacer sentir a cada soldado "
"alemán que vive bajo la boca de un cañón ruso."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/12"
msgid ""
"German artillery has been deployed very close to your position and they are "
"threatening our landings on the Volga. I need you to take them out, Comrades!"
msgstr ""
"La artillería alemana se ha desplegado muy cerca de vuestras posiciones y "
"están amenazando nuestros desembarcos en el Volga. ¡Necesito que los "
"eliminéis, camaradas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/narrator/chuikov/13"
msgid ""
"Good work, Soldiers. I would not have believed such an inferno could open up "
"on earth. Your men died but they did not retreat. Remarkable."
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, soldados. Sus hombres murieron pero no se retiraron. "
"Enhorabuena."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Excellent work! This was a remarkable display of leadership and tenacity. "
"You have defied the odds and successfully prevented the fascists from taking "
"the main prize of their campaign: Stalingrad. You are a true hero of the "
"Soviet Union. Better get your uniform washed and pressed for a ceremony!"
msgstr ""
"Excelente trabajo. Ha sido una notable muestra de liderazgo y tenacidad. "
"Habéis desafiado todas las adversidades y habeis impedido con éxito que los "
"fascistas consigan el premio principal de su campaña: Stalingrado. Usted es "
"un verdadero héroe de la Unión Soviética. Será mejor que haga lavar y "
"planchar su uniforme para las ceremonias de la victoria."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"That is a dramatic end to a dramatic battle. What now? Do we let the "
"fascists take control of Stalingrad? General Chuikov will not like this "
"news. You will have to go in again and this time, hold on to the house. "
"Don’t give up, there is no land beyond the Volga!"
msgstr ""
"Es un final dramático para una batalla dramática. ¿Y ahora qué? ¿Dejamos que "
"los fascistas tomen el control de Stalingrado? Al general Chuikov no le "
"gustará esta noticia. Tendrá que entrar de nuevo y esta vez, poner fin a los "
"fascistas de una vez por todas. ¡No te rindas, no existe la Madre Patria más "
"allá del Volga!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/place"
msgid "13th Guards Rifle Division, 62nd Army"
msgstr "13ª División de Fusileros de la Guardia, 62º Ejército"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/story"
msgid "German army group B has reached Stalingrad, despite Stalin’s order 227 saying “not a step back”. Already in September, street fighting is a grim everyday reality.\n\nThe Soviet 62nd army, commanded by general Chuikov, is hanging on to a few small bridgeheads on the west bank of the Volga river.\n\nIf the Germans want to get to the Volga, they will need to get past Pavlov’s house first!\n\nIn this mission, General Chuikov will brief you on taking the house with your men. As soon as you have full control of the house, prepare every floor and every position for the inevitable next fascist attack. Hold the house long enough for the next wave of supplies to arrive. Show no mercy.\n\nZa Rodinu!"
msgstr ""
"El grupo B del ejército alemán ha llegado a Stalingrado,\n"
"\n"
"a pesar de la orden 227 de Stalin de \"ni un paso atrás\"\n"
"\n"
"Ya en septiembre, los combates callejeros son el día \n"
"\n"
"A día\n"
"\n"
"El 62º ejército soviético, al mando del general Chuikov,\n"
"\n"
"se aferra a algunas pequeñas cabezas de puente en \n"
"\n"
"el oeste del río Volga\n"
"\n"
"Si los alemanes quieren llegar al Volga, necesitarán\n"
"\n"
"pasar primero por la casa de Pavlov.\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"En esta misión, el general Chuikov te informará sobre\n"
"\n"
"tomar la casa con tus hombres\n"
"\n"
"Tan pronto como tengas el objetivo controlado, prepara\n"
"\n"
"cada piso y cada posición para la inevitable próxima\n"
"\n"
"Ofensiva fascista. Mantén la casa a salvo hasta que\n"
"\n"
"lleguen los refuerzos. No mostréis piedad\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"¡Za Rodinu!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/task1"
msgid "Secure the strategic building"
msgstr "Asegurar el edificio estratégico"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/task2"
msgid "Hold the building at all costs!"
msgstr "¡Defiende el edificio a toda costa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/task3"
msgid "Take out the enemy artillery threatening the Volga landings"
msgstr "Elimina la artillería enemiga que amenaza el desembarco en el Volga"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/task4"
msgid "Sergeant Yakov Pavlov must survive!"
msgstr "¡El sargento Yakov Pavlov debe sobrevivir!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/task5"
msgid "Keep Sniper Anatoly Checkov alive."
msgstr "Manten vivo al francotirador Anatoly Checkov."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/task_supply"
msgid "Secure supplies"
msgstr "Asegura los suministros"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/timer"
msgid "German counter-attack in:"
msgstr "Contraataque alemán llegará en:"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_09_pavlovs_house/mission_heal_pavlov"
msgid "Treat Sergeant Yakov Pavlov before he bleeds to death!"
msgstr "Cura al sargento Yakpov Pavlov antes de que se desangre!"